summary: You Sent This Hurricane Now It Won't Go Away Sequel to I’ve Been Hoping You’d Be Somewhere Better Than This By runaway_train...
caption:
You Sent This Hurricane Now It Won’t Go Away

Sequel to I’ve Been Hoping You’d Be Somewhere Better Than This

By runaway_train

“Louis? You’re in charge. Don’t let Harry kill my baby.”

“Sure Gemz,” he grins back.

“I’m not going to kill your baby. Go.” Harry puts a hand on her back and starts pushing her passed the doorframe.

“OK, OK, I’m going,” she says as she waves at all three boys, Louis lifting the youngest one’s arm to help him wave back at his mum.

Once the door is closed and locked behind her, Harry turns around. He slaps both his cheeks with his hands, his eyes wide. He looks like something out of Home Alone. “I’m going to kill her baby aren’t I?”

Louis starts to laugh and turns to walk back into the kitchen. “You’re not going to kill her baby. Now come on, think someone is getting cranky and needs fed. And I’m not talking about the kid.”

Or

The one where Louis knows he has something to say. He just doesn’t know how to say it.

title: 28 Tattoo
body:
To anyone out there who thinks that Louis 28 has nothing to do with Harry let me just deliver you some information.
Louis has 28 tattooed across his left hand on the middle finger and ring finger. 28 is a significant number for Louis, although no one knows exactly why it is believed that something significant happened for Harry and him on the 28.09.2013. Not only that but if you notice Robbie Williams tattoos, he has a similar one, an A on his ring finger of his left hand, this is to signify his wife Ayda Field (Williams), Robbie does not wear a ring and has this instead, why is it so hard to believe that Louis has the 28 tattooed for a similar reason. Also Harry has many rings which he wears and often changes, ones that have represented Louis have been the blue topaz ring that he wore for a few years around 2014/2015/2016 in 2018 we then noticed a newer ring which is often a ring that is gifted on anniversaries 💚💙😊
